\end_inset

 in this expression:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
Pr[\hat{y}_{0}-something\,\leq E[y_{o}|x_{o}]\leq\hat{y}_{0}+something]=0.95
\end{equation}

\end_inset


